Luke Joslyn, rising Sr, looking to fill big shoes of Dan Slotman as #1 player. Excellent driver and solid iron player, his goal will be to qualify for ECIC's. 3 sport athlete whom also excels in the classroom, he will be looked at as the leader of the Eagles in the Fall of 2020.

